❤️cool story to follow...
James @james_sweigert 60th bday @ the Kelly slater Surf Ranch was an amazing blessing and break from the madness that is occurring all around the world. A little over 16 years ago I was newly sober, new to LA and was kicked out of a sober living for a fight, at night. I had a garbage bag full of all my clothes and belongings, and nowhere to go. I called James, he let me crash on his couch. He left his wallet on the kitchen counter, which was the first time in a long time I felt human, and trusted. Fast forward 16 yrs... we got to surf one of the best waves in the world together and although it was much harder to surf than I thought it'd be. And quite ego crushing, it was a dream come true, love you James. Thx for being there for me all these years 👊🏻🫶❤️🙏🏻
